data.title: Health Sciences
data.meta_description: dpo2022-1408 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document authorizes certain DOH officials and personnel to participate in an upcoming Mid-Term Review Mission for the World Bank Philippines COVID-19 Emergency Response Project from April 25-30, 2022. The mission will review the project's performance and implementation progress in Metro Manila, Pangasinan, and the Cordillera Administrative Region. Over 30 officials and staff from various DOH offices are authorized to participate either in-person or virtually in discussion meetings and field visits related to the review.
